title: CITY VIEWS / 4 CLOSETS / STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES / WASHER & DRYER /
posting_body: ['CITY VIEWS / 4 CLOSETS / STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES / WASHER & DRYER / GYM / CONCIERGE', 'Listing ID #: 212858', 'Price: $4,400', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: Studio', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Welcome to your new home!', 'The oversized living area easily fits a full living room and bedroom set.', 'You will be WOWED at every turn in this exquisite residence.', 'Peace and serenity await you while the excitement of the all the city has to offer is right at your doorstep.', 'This prewar rental building combines old New York charm with modern living.', 'Built in 1931, all the homes have been recently renovated and most have unparalleled views of downtown and midtown Manhattan.', 'Building amenities include a 24-hour doorman, on-site resident manager, gym and laundry room.', 'Located in the historic West Village, you are surrounded by cobblestone streets, landmark buildings, hidden square and ivy covered facades.', 'The premier location includes easy access to galleries, cafes, great eateries and boutiques.', 'Getting around town will be a breeze with 1,2,3,A,C,E,M,F,L trains all within a 1 block radius.', 'Come live in this historic area where art and culture are in abundance!', 'For showings contact:', 'Adel Talebpour / The Bouklis Group / 212-961-7334 (cell) / <URL> / <URL> / <URL>', 'Adel Talebpour', 'Phone: 212-402-7855', 'Mobile: 212-961-7334', 'Email: <URL>', 'The Bouklis Group \xa0 212-402-7855 \xa0 212-961-7334 \xa0 <URL>', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Adel Talebpour at 212-961-7334']
